Title: Storm Warning
Description:
Ah, $c! I knew I would find you at the right place at the right time. 

The elements do not just threaten the Dragon Isles in our current time, but also from beyond. Go to the Temporal Conflux and travel through the rift into the future the primalists have overrun.

There, speak to Soridormi. She will have more details for you when you arrive.
ObjectivesText: Speak to Soridormi in the Primalist Future. The portal to the Primalist Future can be found at the Temporal Conflux in Thaldraszus.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Speak to Soridormi in the Primalist Tomorrow.

Objectives.Text: Portal to the Primalist Future taken
